
Sundstrom Hill Winery is a small, boutique family owned wineries winery that sources its fruit from nearby high quality vineyards. The winery has been designed to also serve as a venue for small, special events that give the public the opportunity to enjoy themselves surrounded by barrels, tanks and winemaking equipment. Tastings hours are the first Saturday of every month from 1 p.m.  5:00 p.m. and the second and fourth Thursday of every month from 5 p.m.  7 p.m. Private tastings are also available by appointment.

